Package com.exasol.sql.expression.function.exasol

Class AnalyticFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exasol.sql.expression.function.AbstractFunction
      • com.exasol.sql.expression.function.exasol.AnalyticFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Function, ValueExpression
    public class AnalyticFunction
extends AbstractFunction
    This class represents an analytic function in the Exasol database that supports keywords DISTINCT and ALL and the over clause.
